&lt;p&gt;o Determines project needs, constraints, and responsibilities to meet all of the customer’s HVAC system design and installation requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Effectively writes, presents and communicates bids. Negotiates value and closes the sale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Positively and credibly influences system design and solutions with customers. Frequently creates competitive, high quality and timely estimates, bids, proposals, and cost/benefit analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Manages multiple, ongoing, projects particularly focusing on selling HVAC equipment, service and systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Builds partnering relationships with customers and manufacturers contractors. Understands the customer&#39;s business and speaks their language.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Responsible for supporting and assisting in the accounts receivable collection process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Addresses customer&#39;s operational and environmental objectives, needs and requirements and sell solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Solicits support from and communicates effectively with the entire sales team and inside sales supports staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Assists in the development of the sales team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Keeps management informed of progress and account status. Knows when to call for assistance from upper management to keep the sales process moving.&lt;/p&gt;
