&lt;p&gt;o Willingness to make sales calls and interact with customers outside of the office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Excellent initiative, and interpersonal communications skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o Demonstrated ability to influence the market at key levels.&lt;/p&gt;
